<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Swipe Gesture Test</h1>

    <div class="mb-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        This page is designed to test the swipe gesture functionality for mobile navigation.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-indigo-100/10 dark:bg-indigo-900/10 p-4 rounded-lg border border-indigo-600/20 dark:border-indigo-400/20">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Instructions:</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>On a mobile device, swipe <strong>right</strong> from the left edge of the screen to open the menu.</li>
          <li>When the menu is open, swipe <strong>left</strong> to close it.</li>
          <li>Try swiping from different areas of the screen to test the gesture recognition.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Swipe Area</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
        Try swiping left or right in this area to test the gesture detection.
      </p>

      <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500/20 to-purple-500/20 dark:from-indigo-600/20 dark:to-purple-600/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center">
          <i class="fas fa-arrows-left-right text-2xl mb-2 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"></i>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Swipe here</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
      <div class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Swipe Right</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Swipe from left to right to open the mobile menu.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"></i>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Swipe Left</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          When the menu is open, swipe from right to left to close it.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left text-xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
